│ You are an expert at playing connect-4. The board   │ 5              │ 3.0   │
│ is 7 columns wide and 6 rows high, where each cell  │                │       │
│ can be empty (-), contain an X, or contain an O. To │                │       │
│ indicate a move, respond with the number of the     │                │       │
│ column (1 to 7) where you want to place your mark.  │                │       │
│                                                     │                │       │
│ The game history is given below. Respond only with  │                │       │
│ the next move by indicating the number              │                │       │
│ corresponding to the column where you want to place │                │       │
│ your mark. Do not include any explanations or       │                │       │
